Welcome to Mengis Capital Management





































Jeff Mengis



	With over 20 years of investment experience, Jeff has successfully managed portfolios through three major market corrections and has significant tenure managing portfolios from $1 million to $10 million.  He began his career in 1987 at Black & Co., a Portland based investment banking and security research firm.In 1991, Jeff joined Charter Investment Group, where he was quickly promoted to Vice President.  In 1997, Sutro & Company acquired Charter Investment Group.  Jeff continued with Sutro as a portfolio manager where he developed the investment philosophy and approach that became the cornerstone for the firm he founded in 2001, Mengis Capital Management Inc.



























Welcome to Mengis Capital Management


































Mengis Capital Management, Inc. is an independent Registered Investment Advisory firm in Portland, Oregon. 
Launched in 2001 under the leadership of Jeff Mengis, the firm develops long-term relationships primarily with high net worth individuals through trust, discipline, and consistency.
We specialize in tax-efficient individual equity portfolio management. A strategic asset allocation model structured to provide optimal portfolio performance complements our individual equity process. We tailor portfolios to meet the individual needs of our clients.


   Jeff Mengis
   Cindy Aschbacher
   Michael Patterson





























